targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    week_start_date,
    avg_percent_of_rda || '% (' || weekly_status || ')' AS label
FROM personal_data.weekly_micronutrient_summary
WHERE $__timeFilter(week_start_date) 
  AND  user_id = ${user}
  AND nutrient_name = 'Omega-3 Fatty Acids (mg)'
ORDER BY week_start_date

list.definition:
SELECT DISTINCT u.fatsecret_user_id AS __text, u.id AS __value
FROM personal_data.users u
JOIN personal_data.weights w ON w.user_id = u.id
ORDER BY u.fatsecret_user_id;
list.name: user
list.query:
SELECT DISTINCT u.fatsecret_user_id AS __text, u.id AS __value
FROM personal_data.users u
JOIN personal_data.weights w ON w.user_id = u.id
ORDER BY u.fatsecret_user_id;
